<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>qwlwạ llṣdyq kẖyr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (qwlwạ llṣdyq kẖyr .. rbk fy ạ̹ydyh ạlslṭạn
 mhmạ ạ̹n kạn ạlạ̉mr kẖṭyr .. tḥt jnạḥ ạlrb ạ̉mạn)2
 ạlqrạr- bạʿt ḥạlaⁿạ tlgẖrạf .. byqwlk lyh yạ ạbny tkẖạf
 dạ ạ̹nt rʿyẗ fy wsṭ kẖrạf .. hy qṭyʿy ạlly ạ̉nạ bạḥmyh
 2- (qwlwạ llṣdyq rnm .. wạrfʿ rạsk kdh frḥạn
 tḥt ṣlybk lw mtạ̉lm .. fjr qyạmtk bkrh ybạn)2
 3- (qwlwạ llṣdyq ʿwd .. wạtdẖkr mạḍy ạlạ̹ḥsạn
 hl mn mrẗ ạ̹tmnʿ ạljwd .. ạ̉w byĩt fy ywm jwʿạn)2
 4- (qwlwạ llṣdyq kẖyr .. wạnt f mrḍk ạ̉w tʿbạn
 ẓrfk lw kạn ṣʿb mryr .. sẖwf ạlkẖyr jwạh ạlạ̹ymạn)2</lyrics>
